The paper discusses hyperparameter optimization and neural architecture search using convolutional neural networks on the CIFAR-10 dataset. This falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural networks (cs.NE), and systems and control (cs.SY). However, since the focus is on machine learning and computer vision, cs.LG and cs.CV are the most likely categories, followed by cs.AI and cs.NE, and then cs.SY.
